---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Desarrollo Web en Caracas | Ingeniería de Software | Vortex Logic"
  description="Desarrollo web a medida en Caracas. Creamos aplicaciones web, PWAs e integraciones de API robustas, escalables y ultrarrápidas con Astro y React."
  isLocalBusiness={true}
>
  <!-- ─── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative pt-36 pb-32 overflow-hidden linear-gradient-bg border-b border-[#1f1f24] px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 linear-grid opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[300px] bg-white/[0.015] blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-extralight tracking-tight text-white mb-8 leading-[1.08] max-w-4xl mx-auto opacity-95">
        Desarrollo Web en Caracas: Ingeniería de Software a Medida
      </h1>

      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[#cbd5e1] font-light mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Creamos aplicaciones web progresivas, integraciones de API robustas y plataformas 
        headless que escalan con tu negocio. Astro, React, Next.js y Supabase — 
        el stack definitivo para empresas que exigen rendimiento.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-20">
        <a href="#contacto" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-all text-center duration-200 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)]">
          Cotizar Solución Técnica
        </a>
        <a href="#soluciones" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-white/90 font-medium text-xs rounded-full hover:text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 group transition-colors">
          Ver soluciones <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">➔</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Mockup de consola/API visual -->
      <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="linear-card rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-[#2e2e34] shadow-[0_50px_100px_-20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.98)]">
          <div class="bg-[#08080c] px-4 py-3.5 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#1f1f24]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]/50"></span>
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]/50"></span>
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#27c93f]/50"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/40 flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[10px]">terminal</span>
              vortex-api-server // build:production
            </div>
            <div class="w-12"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 min-h-[420px] bg-[#000000] text-left">
            <!-- Panel izquierdo: editor de código -->
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-8 p-6 border-r border-[#1f1f24] font-mono text-[11px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[10px] text-[#cbd5e1]/60 border-b border-[#1f1f24] pb-3 mb-4">
                <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></span>
                  api/endpoints.ts
                </span>
                <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></span>
                  components/
                </span>
                <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                  <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
                  db/schema.ts
                </span>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-1.5">
                <div><span class="text-purple-400">import</span> { <span class="text-yellow-200">supabase</span> } <span class="text-purple-400">from</span> <span class="text-green-300">'../db/client'</span>;</div>
                <div><span class="text-purple-400">import</span> { <span class="text-yellow-200">defineEndpoint</span> } <span class="text-purple-400">from</span> <span class="text-green-300">'@vortex/api'</span>;</div>
                <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/40">// Endpoint RESTful con validación y rate-limiting</div>
                <br />
                <div><span class="text-blue-400">export const</span> <span class="text-yellow-200">GET</span> = defineEndpoint(<span class="text-purple-400">async</span> (&#123; req, res &#125;) <span class="text-purple-400">=></span> &#123;</div>
                <div class="pl-4"><span class="text-blue-400">const</span> { <span class="text-yellow-200">data</span> } = <span class="text-purple-400">await</span> <span class="text-yellow-200">supabase</span></div>
                <div class="pl-8">.<span class="text-yellow-200">from</span>(<span class="text-green-300">'clientes'</span>)</div>
                <div class="pl-8">.<span class="text-yellow-200">select</span>(<span class="text-green-300">'*'</span>)</div>
                <div class="pl-8">.<span class="text-yellow-200">limit</span>(<span class="text-yellow-400">100</span>);</div>
                <br />
                <div class="pl-4"><span class="text-purple-400">return</span> res</div>
                <div class="pl-8">.<span class="text-yellow-200">status</span>(<span class="text-yellow-400">200</span>)</div>
                <div class="pl-8">.<span class="text-yellow-200">json</span>(&#123; data, meta: &#123; cached: <span class="text-blue-400">true</span>, latency: <span class="text-yellow-400">12ms</span> &#125;&#125;);</div>
                <div>});</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Panel derecho: logs de respuesta API -->
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-4 p-6 bg-[#050507]/30 font-mono text-[10px]">
              <div class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[#cbd5e1]/40 mb-4 font-semibold">Response Log</div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="p-2 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                  <div class="text-green-400">200 OK</div>
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/60">GET /api/clientes</div>
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/40 text-[9px]">12ms · 1420 rows</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-2 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                  <div class="text-green-400">201 Created</div>
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/60">POST /api/contacto</div>
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/40 text-[9px]">8ms · payload 2.4KB</div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-2 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                  <div class="text-yellow-400">304 Not Modified</div>
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/60">GET /api/productos</div>
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/40 text-[9px]">2ms · cached</div>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-[#1f1f24]/50 pt-2 mt-2">
                  <div class="text-[#cbd5e1]/40">Uptime: 99.99%</div>
                  <div class="text-green-500">SSL · WAF · Rate Limited</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── SOLUCIONES AVANZADAS ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="soluciones" class="py-36 px-6 md:px-12 bg-black relative border-b border-[#1f1f24]">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mb-24">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1] uppercase tracking-widest block mb-3 font-medium">Soluciones Avanzadas</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-light text-white tracking-tight leading-snug">
          Arquitectura de software moderna para empresas que necesitan más que un sitio web.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <!-- PWA -->
        <div class="space-y-6 group">
          <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] linear-card rounded border border-[#1f1f24] bg-[#08080c]/30 flex items-center justify-center p-6 glow-hover transition-all">
            <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-[#cbd5e1]/40 group-hover:text-white/80 transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="20" y="10" width="60" height="80" rx="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <rect x="30" y="20" width="40" height="40" rx="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
              <path d="M40 65H60" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="50" cy="48" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
              <path d="M35 80L50 72L65 80" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
              <path d="M50 20V10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="1 1"/>
              <path d="M30 88L50 82L70 88" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="1 1"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2.5">Progressive Web Apps (PWA)</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#cbd5e1] leading-relaxed">
              Transformamos tu web en una experiencia de aplicación nativa con service workers, 
              caché offline, notificaciones push y carga instantánea. Tus usuarios en Caracas 
              acceden a tu plataforma incluso sin conexión a internet.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 mt-3 text-[10px] text-[#cbd5e1] font-mono">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Instalable en home screen</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Sincronización en segundo plano</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> 90% menos datos que app nativa</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- APIs e Integraciones -->
        <div class="space-y-6 group">
          <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] linear-card rounded border border-[#1f1f24] bg-[#08080c]/30 flex items-center justify-center p-6 glow-hover transition-all">
            <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-[#cbd5e1]/40 group-hover:text-white/80 transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M15 50L40 30L40 70L15 50Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <path d="M40 50L65 30L65 70L40 50Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <path d="M65 50L90 30L90 70L65 50Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <circle cx="40" cy="30" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
              <circle cx="65" cy="30" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
              <circle cx="40" cy="70" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
              <circle cx="65" cy="70" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
              <path d="M50 15L50 25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
              <path d="M50 75L50 85" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2.5">Integraciones de API y CRMs</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#cbd5e1] leading-relaxed">
              Conectamos tu web con los sistemas que ya usas: CRMs como Salesforce o HubSpot, 
              pasarelas de pago, ERP contable, sistemas de inventario y cualquier API REST 
              o GraphQL. Flujos automatizados que eliminan procesos manuales.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 mt-3 text-[10px] text-[#cbd5e1] font-mono">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Webhooks en tiempo real</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Autenticación OAuth 2.0 / JWT</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Documentación Swagger/OpenAPI</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bases de Datos Headless -->
        <div class="space-y-6 group">
          <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] linear-card rounded border border-[#1f1f24] bg-[#08080c]/30 flex items-center justify-center p-6 glow-hover transition-all">
            <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-[#cbd5e1]/40 group-hover:text-white/80 transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M50 25L75 38L50 51L25 38L50 25Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <path d="M50 45L75 58L50 71L25 58L50 45Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <path d="M50 65L75 78L50 91L25 78L50 65Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.25"/>
              <path d="M50 25V91" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2"/>
              <circle cx="50" cy="38" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
              <circle cx="50" cy="58" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
              <circle cx="50" cy="78" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2.5">Bases de Datos Headless</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#cbd5e1] leading-relaxed">
              Arquitectura desacoplada con Supabase (PostgreSQL), Airtable o MongoDB. 
              Tu equipo accede y edita los datos desde un panel amigable mientras el frontend 
              consume la información via API. Escalabilidad horizontal sin límites.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 mt-3 text-[10px] text-[#cbd5e1] font-mono">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Realtime subscriptions (WebSockets)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Row Level Security integrado</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-green-400">→</span> Migraciones automatizadas</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── BLOQUE DETALLADO: ARQUITECTURA ─────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-36 px-6 md:px-12 bg-black border-b border-[#1f1f24] relative">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto space-y-44 relative z-10">

      <!-- Bloque: Stack Técnico -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-5">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1] uppercase tracking-widest block font-medium">Stack Técnico</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-light text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
            El stack que usan las startups más innovadoras del mundo.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#cbd5e1] font-light leading-relaxed">
            Astro para velocidad extrema, React para interactividad, Supabase como backend 
            escalable y Vercel para despliegues globales. Cada tecnología es seleccionada 
            por su rendimiento, seguridad y ecosistema. No usamos código legacy ni dependencias 
            innecesarias.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-[#cbd5e1] font-light">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">check_circle</span>
              Astro + React Islands Architecture
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">check_circle</span>
              TypeScript estricto en toda la codebase
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">check_circle</span>
              Testing automatizado (Vitest + Playwright)
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">check_circle</span>
              CI/CD con deploys automáticos desde GitHub
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="linear-card rounded-lg border border-[#1f1f24] overflow-hidden bg-[#08080c]/50 p-8 shadow-2xl relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 font-mono text-[8px] text-[#1f1f24] p-6 select-none overflow-hidden leading-relaxed pointer-events-none opacity-20">
              // Arquitectura<br />
              client → CDN → Edge<br />
              ↓<br />
              Astro SSR + API Routes<br />
              ↓<br />
              Supabase PostgreSQL<br />
              ↓<br />
              WebSocket Realtime
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#1f1f24] pb-4 mb-6 relative z-10">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1] flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></span>
                architecture // vortex-stack
              </span>
              <span class="text-[9px] text-[#cbd5e1]/40 font-mono">Producción</span>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 relative z-10">
              <div class="p-4 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-400 block mb-1">Frontend</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/90">Astro + React + Tailwind</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-400 block mb-1">Backend</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/90">Supabase + API Routes</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-400 block mb-1">Despliegue</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/90">Vercel Edge Network</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded bg-black/40">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-cyan-400 block mb-1">Base de Datos</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/90">PostgreSQL / Airtable</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bloque: Flujo de Datos / Diagrama API -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="linear-card rounded-lg border border-[#1f1f24] overflow-hidden bg-[#08080c]/50 p-6 shadow-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-[#1f1f24] pb-4 mb-4">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1] flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></span>
                data-flow // api-pipeline
              </span>
              <span class="text-[9px] text-[#cbd5e1]/40 font-mono">WebSocket Realtime</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Diagrama de flujo de datos visual -->
            <div class="py-8 px-4 relative z-10">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2">
                <!-- Cliente -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded-lg bg-black/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-white/80">devices</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[8px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/60">Cliente</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1f1f24] to-cyan-500/30 relative">
                  <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[7px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/30">HTTPS</span>
                </div>
                <!-- CDN -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded-lg bg-black/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-cyan-400">cloud</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[8px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/60">Edge CDN</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/30 to-purple-500/30 relative">
                  <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[7px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/30">~12ms</span>
                </div>
                <!-- API Server -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded-lg bg-black/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-purple-400">dns</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[8px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/60">API Server</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/30 to-green-500/30 relative">
                  <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-[7px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/30">SQL</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Database -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 border border-[#1f1f24] rounded-lg bg-black/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">database</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[8px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/60">PostgreSQL</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Línea de tiempo debajo -->
              <div class="mt-6 border-t border-[#1f1f24]/50 pt-3 flex justify-between text-[8px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1]/40">
                <span>Request</span>
                <span>Cache</span>
                <span>Process</span>
                <span>Query</span>
                <span>Response</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-5 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#cbd5e1] uppercase tracking-widest block font-medium">Arquitectura de Datos</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-light text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
            Flujo de datos en tiempo real. Sin cuellos de botella.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#cbd5e1] font-light leading-relaxed">
            Diseñamos sistemas donde los datos viajan del cliente a la base de datos 
            y viceversa en milisegundos. WebSockets para actualizaciones en vivo, 
            caché inteligente en el edge y consultas optimizadas con índices 
            personalizados. Tu equipo siempre ve la información más reciente.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-[#cbd5e1] font-light">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">check_circle</span>
              Subscripciones Realtime con Supabase
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-green-400">check_circle</span>
              Caché distribuido en Vercel Edge
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
